==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Hindustani
<hw>Hindustani</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a native or
inhabitant of Hindustan or India.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hindu, Hindoo.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a form of Hindi spoken around Delhi. See
<er>Hindoostanee</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hindoostani, Hindoostanee, Hindostani.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

